OL,3,CKazuo Ishiguro: I come up with book
OL,4,Ctitles by looking through cookbooks
OL,6,FNobel Prize-winning novelist Sir Kazuo
OL,7,FIshiguro has said he comes up with
OL,8,Fbook titles by looking through
OL,9,Fcookbooks with his wife.
OL,11,FThe Japanese-born author, 69, who
OL,12,Fmoved to the UK as a child, is known
OL,13,Ffor 2005's Never Let Me Go and 1989's
OL,14,FThe Remains Of The Day, for which he
OL,15,Fwon the Man Booker Prize.
