OL,3,CKazuo Ishiguro: I come up with book
OL,4,Ctitles by looking through cookbooks
OL,6,FSpeaking at the Southbank event An
OL,7,FEvening with Kazuo Ishiguro and Stacey
OL,8,FKent, in Queen Elizabeth Hall, London,
OL,9,FSir Kazuo joked that he is "not
OL,10,Fcomplaining about being with his wife"
OL,11,FLorna MacDougall for more than 30
OL,12,Fyears, before explaining that they
OL,13,Fhave spent that time coming up with
OL,14,Fthe names of future books.
