OL,3,CKazuo Ishiguro: I come up with book
OL,4,Ctitles by looking through cookbooks
OL,6,FHe added: "If we're talking and we
OL,7,Fcome across, we just say something
OL,8,Fthat might be a good title, or
OL,9,Factually, (I'm) sorry to admit this,
OL,10,Fbut we actually have this thing where
OL,11,Fwe open the book at random, it could
OL,12,Fbe a random cookery book or something,
OL,13,Fand you stick your finger, you mustn't
OL,14,Flook.
OL,16,F"And then you look to see what phrase
OL,17,Fyou're pointing at and you do this
OL,18,Fabout 30 times, and we come up with
OL,19,Fabout five titles."
