OL,3,CKazuo Ishiguro: I come up with book
OL,4,Ctitles by looking through cookbooks
OL,6,FSir Kazuo also talked about how
OL,7,Fconfused he is by fellow writers who
OL,8,Fdo not know how they will finish a
OL,9,Fbook.
OL,11,F"I'm really surprised that people
OL,12,Fdon't worry more about what happens
OL,13,Fwhen the thing ends," he said.
