OL,3,CKazuo Ishiguro: I come up with book
OL,4,Ctitles by looking through cookbooks
OL,6,F"Because for me, that's always a real
OL,7,Fpriority, often when ... I'm stuck for
OL,8,Fages, because I don't know what to do
OL,9,Fnext, I'm stuck, because I can't quite
OL,10,Fsee how you make this material linger,
OL,11,Fyou know, days, months, years after
OL,12,Fthe reader has experienced it, because
OL,13,Fthat, for me is one of the most
OL,14,Fimportant things.
OL,16,F"And it always amazes me that other
OL,17,Fwriters don't worry about this, maybe
OL,18,Fit's just me, maybe it doesn't matter,
OL,19,F(people) have a great time reading a
OL,20,Fbook (and) forget it."
