OL,6,FHe was asked during the talk about his
OL,7,Fsongwriting for American jazz singer
OL,8,FStacey Kent, which is explored in the
OL,9,Frecently published The Summer We
OL,10,FCrossed Europe In The Rain: Lyrics For
OL,11,FStacey Kent, talking about travel in a
OL,12,Fmore environmentally conscious world.
OL,14,FSir Kazuo said that "travel is so
OL,15,Fingrained in our artistic expressions"
OL,16,Fas an "expression of yearning for new
OL,17,Fthings, or for the sorrow of exile"
OL,18,Famong other ideas.
