OL,3,CKazuo Ishiguro: I come up with book
OL,4,Ctitles by looking through cookbooks
OL,6,F"When human beings first started to
OL,7,Ftell stories and sing songs to each
OL,8,Fother, I bet you travel figured in
OL,9,Fthem," he added.
OL,11,F"I don't think we're going to get to
OL,12,Fnet zero any faster by cutting back on
OL,13,Fartistic references but I think that
OL,14,Fif you're right, we do have to be
OL,15,Fperhaps... we should be more conscious.
OL,17,F"(Jim) Tomlinson and Ishiguro songs
OL,18,Ftend to celebrate trams and trains, I
OL,19,Fhave to say, rather than air travel."
