OL,6,FThe Remains Of The Day was his third
OL,7,Fnovel and was adapted into a film
OL,8,Fstarring Sir Anthony Hopkins and Emma
OL,9,FThompson, which earned them both
OL,10,FAcademy Award nominations, and the
OL,11,F1993 adaptation a total of eight Oscar
OL,12,Fnods.
OL,14,FSir Kazuo is also a film writer and
OL,15,Fwrote the Oscar-nominated screenplay
OL,16,Ffor the 2022 film Living, about a
OL,17,Fcivil servant, played by Bill Nighy,
OL,18,Fwho embraces life after he finds out
OL,19,Fhe is dying.
